Quote: MCGREGOR A Dog's Life 23 There are two types of leading dogs. One is the dog that is capable of getting the sheep to follow while he leads in the front of the mob, and the other is known as the wing leader. The latter will take the lead when necessary but will also run back to keep the wing of the mob on either side from drifting.
